<h2>heavy: Robust Estimation Using Heavy-Tailed Distributions</h2>
<p>Functions to perform robust estimation considering heavy-tailed distributions.
    Currently, the package includes routines for linear regression, linear mixed-effect
    models, Grubbs' model, multivariate location and scatter estimation, multivariate
    regression, penalized splines, random variate generation and some support functions.</p>
